Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.61,0:00:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.28,0:00:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the city of Toras?\NThe sun is setting.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.11,0:00:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll rest here tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.91,0:00:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Silver? You must also be dying \Nto smell a woman again after all this time, right? {onna as a human woman specifically, not a mane, idk why a horse would want that}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.08,0:00:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Silver?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.79,0:01:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm dying too! {/can't wait}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.21,0:01:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya, Silver!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.26,0:01:15.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He came down to us from the pages of a children's book, the legendary knight Yamato Takeru. {lit: swordsman from a fairy tale}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.97,0:01:20.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A hardworking hero, who was born as a child of the gods, but must now wander the human realm. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.18,0:01:22.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Though he himself does not know it,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.94,0:01:28.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the fame of his many heroic deeds has already spread across the land, and his name is known everywhere. {lit: crossed fields and mountains}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.69,0:01:32.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The people await his arrival \Nwith eager anticipation.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.28,0:01:34.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hero of the Sun, Yamato Takeru.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.45,0:01:36.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Flaming Swordsman, Yamato Takeru.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.70,0:01:39.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Who hasn't heard of Yamato Takeru? {they named him after https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yamato_Takeru}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.56,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So that's the famous Toras cathedral, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Really is a prosperous city.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.32,0:02:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody grab that brat!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.04,0:02:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thief!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, coming through!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.46,0:02:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You punk...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.05,0:02:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand back what you stole.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and hand it over.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.97,0:02:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I don't know!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.85,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You little street rat, \Nalways picking the pockets... {???? no clue; We should just kill him! in m74}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.15,0:02:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him go! {I assume they all think it's a boy}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.98,0:02:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys get your kicks roughing up \Nkids who can't defend themselves, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky, pal. \NYou might get hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.70,0:03:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just trying to get \Nback what this brat stole.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.58,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No sudden moves.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.03,0:03:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You amateurs won't be able \Nto take me on for as long as you live. {100 years too early}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stole something, hand it over now.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.62,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise I'll let these \Nscary gentlemen deal with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There, that settles it, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you want more?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No... As long as we get this back... Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Yes, the Bishop'll be happy. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.85,0:04:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Don't say more than you have to!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way! Move it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, you brat!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.24,0:04:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I never let my guard down, \Nso I'd like my wallet back.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.12,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I did. You haven't been in this business long, have you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.21,0:04:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really that bad at it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.29,0:04:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Since even I could catch you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.13,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep that up and one day \Nthey'll catch you and lop off both your arms.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.14,0:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You hungry?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Haven't eaten in three days.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll get you something to eat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.52,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.85,0:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but you gotta promise me one thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Promise what?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're with me, no stealing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! I won't even look at your wallet again.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just mine. Nobody's.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.58,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jody. {wiki says "ジョディス" is Jodiceu - i wonder where that su go}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.29,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Takeru.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.63,0:05:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That looks great! \NI could eat her here and now! {lit: delicious - but he says it about the girl}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.68,0:05:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takeru, what about the food you promised?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just gimme a minute. \NWe'll eat after.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's even yummier!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.95,0:05:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru, when are you actually gonna feed me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.28,0:05:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, kid, later! It's women! I haven't had \Na woman in ages! Look at her sticking it out! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.72,0:06:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{this sounds like it's made up of japanese characters, but it's not anything meaningful}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Incubus Leonardo... {muma is incubus; succubus; demon appearing in a dream}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.66,0:07:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunther, I enjoyed this last selection. {ルンター}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the flow of women for me steady!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.25,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, Lord Leonardo, the city of Toras \Nwill soon be completely under my sway,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a den of pure debauchery.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.55,0:07:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep at it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.69,0:07:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.48,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's us, Bishop. {asshira?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you found him? {I assume jody stole money from him and the two gave chase? idk what else they could find}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.66,0:07:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Deliver these women\Nto Vanessa the moneylender. {not on wiki, idk what her name is exactly, venezza?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.84,0:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Top-quality goods.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No... it's gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.26,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear we didn't pocket a single coin!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.26,0:08:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! I'm not talking about money!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The special potion I kept here—\Nthe packet is missing! {wrap/sachet}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The special potion?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that brat must've...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.07,0:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Find him. Find him no matter what.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.28,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows too much, \Nwe can't let him live.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.95,0:08:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him if you have to, but bring it back.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.53,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Find the one who stole the potion immediately!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.30,0:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem troubled, Bishop.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That voice... Shade! {not in wiki}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shade?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.90,0:09:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Creepy as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.69,0:09:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Leonardo send me to keep an eye on you. \NCan't let you out of my sight.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.49,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should understand, \Nif I don't get that potion back,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.62,0:09:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,my true identity \Nwill be exposed to the whole city.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.25,0:09:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't reported anything \Nto Lord Leonardo as of yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.63,0:09:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you, recover that potion for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.05,0:09:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, as long as I can handle it my way.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.93,0:09:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No time to even breathe...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you sure eat a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.94,0:09:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal! \NThis'll last me for two or three days.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.90,0:09:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For a kid who's supposedly had it rough, \Nyou sure can pack it away.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.82,0:09:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really come here to worship \Nand get separated from your sister? {did you ... come ... and get ... - tense coordination}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.20,0:09:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where she is now?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.91,0:09:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she's somewhere in this city, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.20,0:10:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Guess I'll lend you a hand. {pitch in and help}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.41,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.33,0:10:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Toras is big, but if you still can't find her,\Nsomething must've happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.21,0:10:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe some bad guys \Ntricked her and snatched her.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.72,0:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister... she good-looking?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you thinking, you perv?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.10,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew what was on your mind \Neven before you bought me food.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That so? Then this'll be quick.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.65,0:10:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I look at your face, it's not half-bad, \Nso your sister's gotta be pretty decent too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.20,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And if she's not pretty, \Nyou won't go looking for her?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.12,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me your sis...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is too ugly to even look at!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.37,0:10:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I'm telling you, you won't find a girl \Nin this city as gorgeous as my sister!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then it's settled!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.75,0:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if you find her, \NI can't pay you back or anything. {lit: can't thank you}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.88,0:10:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that. \NIf we find her, I'll get plenty of thanks from her. {think he means he'll seduce her and not that "that alone would be enough a reward"}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.39,0:10:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks, Takeru.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.93,0:11:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm not sure if that's kindness \Nor just ulterior motives...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.06,0:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you doubt me like that, \Npartner. Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.90,0:11:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw how you helped that kid earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got real skill.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.61,0:11:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, that was pure luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.86,0:11:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. I can swing a sword myself. \NI can tell you're no amateur.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.91,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use your help.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.25,0:11:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sorry, but I just got hired by this kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.42,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.71,0:11:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Too bad. \NThen some other time.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Julius. {yurius, not in wiki, not sure if a closer match can be found}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.43,0:11:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yamato Takeru.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamato Takeru?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.27,0:11:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not... the one who lifted the curse from Strawberry Fields?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nah, wrong guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really look that strong to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,True...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.86,0:11:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the hero Yamato Takeru \Nis said to be a towering warrior,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.99,0:12:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,an absolute legend, \Nbeloved and respected by all who meet him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially women,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.74,0:12:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,who are overcome with an urge to throw themselves at him the moment they lay eyes on him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.63,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. Damn it, that rumor's taken on a life of its own.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.89,0:12:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You look just like someone I knew.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.43,0:12:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's already dead, \Nso you can't be her.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.27,0:12:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That has to be just an accidental resemblance.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.48,0:12:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They say every face has got \Nthree or four lookalikes in the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess. But...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.49,0:12:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Takeru. When you finish your business with him, come to see me about this job.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if I feel like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Takeru. I'll also head out then.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to find a place to sleep, obviously.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What if those thugs from earlier see you again?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.38,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, shopkeeper.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be staying for a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.14,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.93,0:13:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly. Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.60,0:13:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, find some used clothes that'll fit this kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.23,0:13:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything's better than what he's wearing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got my son's old clothes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.99,0:13:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna share a room with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, bro.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.03,0:13:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm straight as an arrow—\NI'm not swinging that way for as long as I live.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.70,0:13:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! What are you doing?! \NLet go, Takeru!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly. Your room is on the second floor.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.63,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on already, Jody.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Jody?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's here?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, boss? {aniki}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.97,0:13:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's stupidly strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wait till he's asleep, and then...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.77,0:13:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope this works...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Once he's out, he's ours.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That door leads to the bath.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.78,0:14:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Jody, go take a bath first.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.08,0:14:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way, I'm not taking a bath!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.95,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you clean up, nobody will recognize you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.71,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And this inn doesn't want you dirtying up the bed.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.25,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But... I kind of have a cold, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.01,0:14:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep whining and I'll strip you naked \Nand toss you in myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.47,0:14:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No... W-Wait...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, move it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.56,0:14:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, okay! I'll do it myself! Just let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.48,0:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then hurry up and get in.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.81,0:14:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, but don't you dare open the door!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.23,0:14:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell wants to see you naked, idiot?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.16,0:14:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, who raised that guy like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Skittish like a girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Innkeeper.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.86,0:14:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.63,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like a room as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the one next to those boys vacant?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.63,0:15:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is. I'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.23,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought a change of clothes. {for jody, I assume}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.65,0:16:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not much, but it's all I have.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.82,0:16:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is perfect.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.37,0:16:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Jody'll look presentable in this.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.66,0:16:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jody!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.00,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your clothes are here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.43,0:16:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look! Don't come in!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You...!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.94,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Stupid Takeru! {???? maybe "get out"}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get out already!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're a girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.45,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru! Get it together, Takeru.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.58,0:16:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru, talk to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru. Takeru?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Takeru?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boobs...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.35,0:17:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Jody, y-you...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.81,0:17:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.48,0:17:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were dead.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.36,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,J-J-Jody, calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I—I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! That must've hurt, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.87,0:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that, Jody, \Njust put some clothes on.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.20,0:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get yourself together, Jody... {lit: told you it's no good}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.23,0:18:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Make love to me, Takeru... {daite means fuck me}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hold it...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.28,0:18:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't right, Jody. \NYou can't be doing stuff like this yet. {meaning she's too young}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.41,0:18:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. \NYou saved me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.37,0:18:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... This and that aren't the same thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said you'd help me find my sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.25,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I did, but still...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.05,0:18:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.95,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you my sister's a real looker, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.14,0:18:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.60,0:18:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want my sister stealing you away from me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.15,0:18:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Didn't see that coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.03,0:18:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That filthy little brat was a girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.95,0:19:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If we'd grabbed her earlier, \Nwe'd be the ones with her now...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that nice ass on her.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.83,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two that much into that little girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Shade!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the one who stole the potion?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.80,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.80,0:19:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the man?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.93,0:19:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems he's a wandering headhunter. \NHe's damn good with that sword. {????? no clue what's that uraebo}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.56,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! You can't stop \Nin the middle of it, silly Takeru!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.73,0:19:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, hold on. \NI can't even breathe like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.69,0:19:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.28,0:19:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you must think I'm shameless.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.87,0:19:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it, Jody.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.49,0:19:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... My bad. \NSo what's your actual name?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.83,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice. {that answers it}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice name.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.75,0:19:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice, I've already gotten \Nplenty of advance payment.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.09,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We start searching for your sister tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.18,0:19:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So tonight you're going to sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.68,0:20:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A mercenary taking full payment \Nbefore the job even starts is weird, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.93,0:20:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happened earlier \Nwas just the down payment for the job.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.60,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate me, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.94,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's not because hate you. \NYou're cute, Jodice. {...[that I didn't fuck you]}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.20,0:20:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.12,0:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.53,0:20:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we save your sister, \NI'll come for the rest of the reward.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That work for you, Jodice?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru, you're mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.17,0:20:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I like women, Jodice.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.59,0:20:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But taking advantage of a girl I saved to get in her bed?\NThat'd weigh on me a bit. {lit: using favors to bed girls? I'd feel guilty}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.72,0:20:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take just a little more down payment.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.70,0:21:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.70,0:21:08.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,W-Well... if you insist... {/I'll take you up on that offer}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.92,0:21:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss me, Takeru.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.84,0:21:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you, Jodice.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me too...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.56,0:21:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.37,0:21:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.26,0:22:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru! Takeru!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.09,0:22:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.60,0:23:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice view.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.52,0:23:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.19,0:23:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our line!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.24,0:23:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Make one wrong move and the girl \Ngets a pretty red flower blooming on her throat.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.20,0:23:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That what you want?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.58,0:23:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodice!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.96,0:23:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.42,0:24:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say "Takeru"?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.21,0:24:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the sword down, or else...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.13,0:24:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.10,0:24:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.14,0:24:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.14,0:24:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, set it down nice and slow.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.81,0:24:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, just don't hurt Jodice.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.45,0:24:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:30.66,0:24:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make such loud noises. \NClose the door.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:33.54,0:24:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:41.04,0:24:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:03.40,0:25:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak up, girly. \NWhere's the stuff you swiped earlier?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.90,0:25:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us quick or I'll slice your ear clean off.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:10.20,0:25:13.66,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Stop! I don't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:14.20,0:25:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe you'd prefer a pretty red flower?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.08,0:25:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Takeru...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:21.25,0:25:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Still nothing?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:23.13,0:25:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:25.13,0:25:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did she hide it?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:27.92,0:25:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Something happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:29.84,0:25:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. We've been interrupted. \NWe're pulling out.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:33.22,0:25:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking the girl and her clothes. Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:35.64,0:25:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:39.98,0:25:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:52.74,0:25:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:54.20,0:25:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with me! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:22.02,0:26:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, where'd she hide it?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:33.86,0:26:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:35.24,0:26:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:39.74,0:26:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early to start screaming.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:45.83,0:26:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You two find anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:48.55,0:26:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:50.63,0:26:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:52.63,0:26:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we'll have \Nto work it out of your body then.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:04.98,0:27:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There, see?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:08.94,0:27:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It... It hurts! {?? why?}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:11.32,0:27:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:13.19,0:27:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then speak up!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:14.36,0:27:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:19.95,0:27:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Please, stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:31.75,0:27:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, talk.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:33.55,0:27:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the item you stole from the Bishop?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:37.18,0:27:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I—I gave it back.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:46.31,0:27:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:47.48,0:27:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You took something out of it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:49.65,0:27:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the truth or...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:53.69,0:27:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:04.45,0:28:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Help... {tasukete?}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:06.75,0:28:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop, don't twist them! {???}
