Dialogue: 10,0:42:50.51,0:42:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to neutralize the potion?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:53.18,0:42:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Looks like she's back to normal now.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:56.47,0:42:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out on a journey.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:58.18,0:43:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, won't you come with me to the town of Rona? \NSeeing as you're taking care of Jodice now, please! {???? dunno what she means by "accepted Jodice's thing"}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:05.77,0:43:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The town of Rona, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:08.19,0:43:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it. {/accept it [the job]}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:09.40,0:43:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go on ahead and wait for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:14.20,0:43:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really were the princess.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:16.24,0:43:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're the daughter \Nof the palace forest watchman. {rikyuu is  imperial villa; royal villa; detached palace}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:19.49,0:43:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Do you remember now?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:22.33,0:43:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister suffered so much, \Nit makes my heart ache.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:26.46,0:43:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Bishop dead, \Nthis town should know peace again.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:30.50,0:43:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:32.51,0:43:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:33.51,0:43:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm returning to Talos Castle.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:35.84,0:43:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Until Leonardo is defeated, \Nthere will be no peace in this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:40.68,0:43:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Takeru?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:44.31,0:43:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He left on his journey.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:46.06,0:43:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I hope to ask for his help once more.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:48.11,0:43:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:52.07,0:43:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. {for what? maybe wakarimashita somehow implies "understood, he's your man now"?}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:59.87,0:44:05.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Free-spirited and hungry for thrills, the wandering swordsman Yamato Takeru keeps traveling on.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:05.87,0:44:12.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not knowing the truth of his own birth, \Nhe continues his journey, carrying the star of fate.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:12.63,0:44:17.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is also a hero who chases romance and pleasure—the ultimate adventurer.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:17.80,0:44:24.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What new trials await Yamato Takeru \Non the perilous road ahead? {波乱万丈}
